#OpenKraken-graph HOWTO-test

***
Simple test
***

0. Ensure you have the whole OpenKraken directory, otherwise you won't have CxxTest.
1. compile and install libOpenKN-graph (see HOWTO-build)
2. cd libOpenKN-graph/tests/
3. make
4. enjoy \o/
